name: perm.base.calendar.shared.readonly
condition: (?1) in (SELECT setting.sharedWith FROM self.sharingSettingList setting WHERE setting.visible = true AND setting.rights = 1) OR self.user = (?1)

name: perm.base.calendar.shared.modification
